son|2019\u201320]]<ref name=\"Soccerway\"/>\n|Premier League\n|28||1||1||0||0||0||8{{efn|name=UCL}}||1||4{{efn|One appearance in [[FA Community Shield]]; one appearance in [[UEFA Super Cup]], two appearances in [[FIFA Club World Cup]]|name=|group=}}||0||41||2\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!86!!2!!2!!0!!1!!0!!26!!1!!4!!0!!119!!3\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!255!!10!!13!!2!!16!!1!!26!!1!!11!!1!!321!!15\n|}\n\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 13 October 2019}}<ref>{{NFT player|id=54762|name=Andrew Robertson}}</ref><ref>{{SFA profile|63749|name=Andrew Robertson}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=6|[[Scotland national football team|Scotland]]\n|2014||5||1\n|-\n|2015||3||0\n|-\n|2016||4||0\n|-\n|2017||8||1\n|-\n|2018||8||0\n|-\n|2019||6||1\n|-\n! colspan=2|Total!!34!!3\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''As of match played 8 June 2019. Scotland score listed first, score column indicates score after each Robertson goal.''<ref name = \"eng goal\"/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ International goals by date, venue, opponent, score, result and competition\n|-\n!scope=col|No.\n!scope=col|Date\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Cap\n!scope=col|Opponent\n!scope=col|Score\n!scope=col|Result\n!scope=col|Competition\n|-\n!scope=row|1\n||18 November 2014||[[Celtic Park]], Glasgow, Scotland||align=center|5||{{fb|ENG}}||align=center|1\u20132||align=center|1\u20133||[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]\n|-\n!scope=row|2\n||1 September 2017||[[LFF Stadium]], Vilnius, Lithuania||align=center|16||{{fb|Lithuania}}||align=center|2\u20130||align=center|3\u20130||[[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n!scope=row|3\n||8 June 2019||[[Hampden Park]], Glasgow, Scotland||align=center|30||{{fb|Cyprus}}||align=center|1\u20130||align=center|2\u20131||[[UEFA Euro 2020 qualification]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'