ys of John Lennon|isbn=978-1-55972-084-7|publisher=Birch Lane Press|year=1991|ref=CITEREFSeaman1991}}\n* {{cite book|first=David|last=Sheff|authorlink=David Sheff|year=2000|origyear=1981|title=All We Are Saying: The Last Major Interview with John Lennon and Yoko Ono|publisher=St. Martin's Press|location=New York, NY|isbn=0-312-25464-4|ref=harv|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/allwearesayingla00lenn}}\n* {{cite news|author=Shennan, Paddy|work=The Liverpool Echo|title=What will Liz think of these?|date=26 November 2007|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/liverpool-life/liverpool-lifestyle/2007/11/26/what-will-liz-think-of-these-100252-20163545/|accessdate=10 May 2010|ref=CITEREFShennan2007}}\n* {{cite web|author=Songwriters Hall of Fame|year=2015|title=John Lennon|url=http://songwritershalloffame.com/exhibits/C115|accessdate=23 November 2015|ref=harv|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424063437/http://songwritershalloffame.com/exhibits/C115|archivedate=24 April 2012}}\n* {{cite book|last=Spizer|first=Bruce|title=The Beatles Solo on Apple Records|publisher=498 Productions|location=New Orleans, LA|year=2005|isbn=978-0-9662649-5-1|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|author=Spitz, Bob|year=2005|title=The Beatles: The Biography|url=https://archive.org/details/beatlesbiography00spit|url-access=registration|publisher=Little, Brown|isbn=978-0-316-80352-6|ref=CITEREFSpitz2005|author-link=Bob Spitz}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,843470,00.html|title=Other noises, Other notes|date=3 March 1967|work=Time|accessdate=27 November 2010|ref=CITEREFTime1967}}\n* {{cite book|author=The Beatles|year=2000|title=The Beatles Anthology|publisher=Chronicle Books|isbn=978-0-8118-2684-6|ref=CITEREFThe Beatles2000|author-link=The Beatles|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/beatlesanthology0000unse}}\n* {{cite web|publisher=The Brit Awards|title=The Brits 1982|url=http://www.brits.co.uk/history/shows/1