ocumentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1971\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Up Your Legs Forever''\n| none\n| Producer, director\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1971\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Erection (film)|Erection]]''\n| none\n| Short film, producer, director\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1971\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Clock''\n| Himself / Singer\n| Music, writer, producer, director\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1971\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Sweet Toronto]]''\n| Himself\n| Concert film\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1971\n! scope=\"row\"| ''The Museum of Modern Art Show''\n| Himself\n| Documentary short\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1972\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[John Sinclair Freedom Rally|Ten for Two: The John Sinclair Freedom Rally]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1972\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Eat the Document]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1976\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Michel Auder|Chelsea Girls with Andy Warhol]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1977\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Day the Music Died]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1982\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Compleat Beatles]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1988\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Imagine: John Lennon]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|1990\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Beatles: The First U.S. Visit]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1996\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Rolling Stones Rock and Roll Circus]]''\n| Himself\n| Concert film from 1968\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2003\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Lennon Legend: The Very Best of John Lennon (DVD)|Lennon Legend: The Very Best of John Lennon]]''\n| Himself\n| Remastered music video collection\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2006\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The U.S. vs. John Lennon]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| style=